# Cursor BLOCKS these from AI access entirely (not just indexing) — keep only
# paths that never belong in AI context: build output, logs, local runtime
# scratch. Tracked-but-heavy assets (traces, regression tests, packs) live in
# .cursorindexingignore instead, so agents can still open them when the
# bug-lock workflow (AGENTS.md) requires it.
node_modules/
dist/
coverage/
ai-runs/
blind-tester/reports/
.agent-cleaner/
.codex/*
!.codex/config.toml
saves/
transcripts/
*.log
*.tmp
*.tsbuildinfo
